Landing page create by “Google Sites”

- Open Browser
- Go to “Google Sites”
- Login

Step-1
----------
For new design:
- Click on “Blank” page
 
Step-2
----------
Change Theme:
 
- Click on “Theme”
 
- Select “Impression”

Step-3
----------
Change Title:

Step-4
----------
Add column for image and description 
- Click on “Insert” menu
- Choose a "content block"
 
Step-5
---------- 
Add Image:
-	Click on plus (+) button
-	Click on “Upload”
-	Select your image to upload

Step-6
----------
To adjust image
- Click on “Crop” icon
-Trace (টানা) the image to the bottom
 
Step-7
----------
Add Text:
- Add text to right side
- Set “Text font” style
- Set “Font size”
 
Step-8
----------
Add Button:
- Click on “Insert” menu (top right)
- Type your button name
- Copy and paste offer link
 
Step-9
----------
Add Social media comment for more trust:
- Click on “image” icon
- click on "Upload"
- Select images
 
Step-10
----------
After finish all task, you can see full preview:
- Click on “Screen” icon at the top
You will see full page

Step-11
----------
To see your design in different screen
- Click on screen (Desktop, Mobile, Tab)
 
Step-12
----------
Publish Your Site:
- Click on “Publish” button
- Give a name of this site
- Click on “Publish” button
 
Step-13
----------
To get website link:
- Click on “share” icon at the top
- You will get landing page link
